<Layout title={title}>
<h2>Project 4: Small Business Website (240 points)</h2>
<h3>Project Description:</h3>
<p>
  For your final project, you are to create a small business website for “Brews
  & Bonds” coffee shop (Don't like the name? Propose new one!). You can use the
  content here: <a href={ "/assets/project-4-content.pdf" }>project-4-content.pdf</a>. This
  project should exhibit the skills you have developed in this class.
</p>
<h3>Process:</h3>

<strong>Research</strong>
  <ol>
    <li>
      Find and critique three similar (3) websites. Submit
      your critiques on D2L.<br />
    </li>
  </ol>
<strong>Design</strong>
  <ol>
    <li>Create a sitemap in FigJam outlining the pages of your site</li>
    <li>Create a wireframe in Figma of your interface</li>
    <li>
      Photograph, illustrate, or find Creative Commons-licensed images to
      incorporate into your design
    </li>
    <li>
      Establish a brand color palette of at least 5 colors and use these in an
      SVG logo
    </li>
    <li>Design your site in Figma responsively and link on D2L<br /></li>
  </ol>
 <strong>Development</strong>
<ol start="3" type="1">
  <ol start="1" type="a">
    <li>
      Your finished project should be responsive and published to GitHub pages
      and linked on D2L
    </li>
  </ol>
</ol>
